<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich III. von Aufseß, Bischof von Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat beglückwünscht den Adressaten zu seiner Wahl zum Bischof von Bamberg und kündigt Berthold N., Vikar in Nürnberg, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_294" id="146r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_294_r1l2"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> erweltem <expan>Bıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> ʒu Bamberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_294_r1l3"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vnd erwırdıge <expan>p<ex>er</ex>ſon</expan> von <expan>ſchıku<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l4">gabe des <expan>allmechtıg<ex>en</ex></expan> gots ʒu der <expan>wırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> des Bıſtums ʒu Bamberg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l5"><expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vnd erwelet ıſt . das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır mıt <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>frewde<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l6">wolgefallen <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd <expan>wünſche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>furſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ſelıkeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l7">gelük vnd haıle / Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>dıenſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd mıt fleıſſ / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l8">Jr vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wellet <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l9">ſeyn . günſtıge <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> tun vnd <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>amptleẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l10">ʒutun <expan>befelhe<ex>n</ex></expan> / als wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> wol getrawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l11"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> auch <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> / den <expan>erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Bercht<ex>old</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l12"><expan>vıcary<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns dem wır befolhen <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / ettlıch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> meynung </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l13">mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu reden / Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade . was </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l14"><expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Bercht<ex>old</ex></expan> in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l15">an eẅr gnade werbe daʒ Jr Jm das <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l16">nach notdurft der ſache <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beweıſen wellet / Denn wo wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l17"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> / dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r1l18"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij <hi rend="sup"> a </hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Petrȷ et Paulȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_294" id="146r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, erweltem <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan>
                        zu Bamberg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
                        und erwirdige <expan>p<ex>er</ex>son</expan> von
                            <expan>schiku<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und gabe des
                                <expan>allmechtig<ex>en</ex></expan> gots zu der
                                <expan>wirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> des bistums zu Bamberg
                                <expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> und erwelet ist, das
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir mit
                            <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewde<ex>n</ex></expan> und wolgefallen
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>, und <expan>wünsche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>furstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> selikeit, gelük und haile und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>dienstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und mit fleiss, daz ir uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wellet <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        lassen seyn, günstige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> tun und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>amptlewt<ex>en</ex></expan> und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> zu
                        tun <expan>befelhe<ex>n</ex></expan>, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> wol getrawen.
                            <expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, auch <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> den <expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Bercht<ex>old</ex></expan>, <expan>vicary<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns,
                        dem wir befolhen <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, ettlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> meynung mit
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu reden, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade, was
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Bercht<ex>old</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade werbe, daz ir im das
                                <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben und nach notdurft der
                        sache <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beweisen wellet. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <hi rend="sup"> a </hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Petri et Pauli.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
